+ Class Methods

++ Public

* Solar_Form::__construct() -- Constructor.

* Solar_Form::addFeedback() -- Adds multiple feedback messages to elements.

* Solar_Form::addFilter() -- Adds a Solar_Filter method callback for an element.

* Solar_Form::addValid() -- Adds a Solar_Valid method callback as a validation for an element.

* Solar_Form::getStatus() -- Gets the current form status.

* Solar_Form::load() -- Loads form attributes and elements from an external source.

* Solar_Form::orderElements() -- Reorders the existing elements.

* Solar_Form::populate() -- Populates form elements with specified values.

* Solar_Form::reset() -- Resets the form object to its originally-configured state.

* Solar_Form::setElement() -- Sets one element in the form.  Appends if element does not exist.

* Solar_Form::setElements() -- Sets multiple elements in the form.  Appends if they do not exist.

* Solar_Form::setStatus() -- Forcibly sets the form status.

* Solar_Form::validate() -- Performs filtering and validation on each form element.

* Solar_Form::values() -- Returns the form element values as an array.

Inherited Methods:

* Solar_Base::apiVersion() -- Reports the API version for this class.

* Solar_Base::locale() -- Looks up locale strings based on a key.

++ Protected

* Solar_Form::_populate() -- Recursive method to map the submitted values into elements.

* Solar_Form::_prepareName() -- Prepares a name as an array key, if needed.

* Solar_Form::_values() -- Recursively pulls values from elements into an associative array.

Inherited Methods:

* Solar_Base::_exception() -- Convenience method for returning exceptions with localized text.

++ Private

None.